        "jsonBody": "={\n  \"model\": \"{{'gpt-4.1-mini'}}\",\n  \"input\": [\n    {\n      \"role\": \"system\",\n      \"content\": \"You are a LinkedIn content writer. Create a detailed, engaging LinkedIn post summary (4-6 sentences, 1 short paragraph). Highlight key insights, implications, and practical takeaways. Do NOT include the URL inside post_text. Instead, the post_link field MUST begin exactly with: \\\"Read more here: \\\" followed by the full article URL. Return ONLY valid JSON with keys: post_text (string), post_link (string), hashtags (array of strings), safety_ok (boolean), notes (string). No markdown.\"\n    },\n    {\n      \"role\": \"user\",\n      \"content\": \"Slack message:\\n{{ $json.raw_text }}\"\n    }\n  ]\n}\n",
